The Chessable Sunway Sitges is a 10-round Swiss tournament taking place from 12–22 December 2022 in Sitges, Spain.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.sunwaychessfestival.com
